      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like im just stuck in this stupid loop. every time i think i finally got my life together—a job, maybe a decent friend, feeling sober—it just falls apart again. it's like i'm wired to fail. i'm just exhausted from trying to fix something that's fundamentally broken.",
